{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% set page = 'business' %}
{% block body %}
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="card grey darken-4 small">
                    <div class="card-content white-text lighten-4">
                        <h2 style="font-size:3rem;font-style:italic;letter-spacing: 6px;line-height: 3rem;">
                            Business Stay</h2>
                        <h5 class="text-grey">Book your business accommodation with us, today!</h5>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="index-banner" class="col s12 m6 l8">
                <div class="card small" style="overflow:hidden;">
                    {#<div class="card-image">#}
                    <div class="responsive-img"
                         style="
                     height: 100%;
                     background-image: url('/assets/images/Communal/2.jpg');
                     background-repeat: no-repeat;
                     background-position: center;
                     /*background-attachment: fixed;*/
                     background-size: cover;
                 ">
                        <div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-text">
            <p>Each of our apartments are modernise with high-spec decorated and offers guests a warm, comfortable and
                luxury stay. If you are planning a longer business trip and considering extended stay, please contact us
                and
                we will try our best to meet your needs.
            <p>With each apartment are fully equipped with an open plan kitchenette/ living area, modern bathrooms, we
                combines the key comforts of a hotel with the privacy and convenience of your own home. Benefits include
                a
                weekly maid service alone with towel and linen change. More regular housekeeping can also be provided if
                required.
            <p>Book your business accommodation with us, today!
            <p><strong>Please note:</strong> We have room for groups of colleagues and can arrange block bookings.
                Please provide details in
                your enquiry form.
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock body %}